# <Project> — Dependency Update Policy

**Stage D artifact, опциональный.** Cadence + automerge rules для dependency bumps. Применяется ко всем `package.json` / `pyproject.toml` / `Cargo.toml` / `go.mod` / etc. Использует Dependabot / Renovate / эквивалент.

---

## 1. Categories + cadence

| Update type | Cadence | Auto-merge | Review depth |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Security patches (known CVE)** | ASAP — as soon as advisory published | ✅ Yes (если CI green) | Minimal — CVE patch trusted |
| **Patch versions** (semver `X.Y.Z+1`, no CVE) | Weekly batch | ✅ Yes (если CI green) | Minimal — semver promises no breakage |
| **Minor versions** (`X.Y+1.0`) | Biweekly review | ⚠ Manual merge after smoke test | Read changelog, smoke test critical paths |
| **Major versions** (`X+1.0.0`) | Quarterly evaluation | ❌ Manual, dedicated PR | Read migration guide, plan expand-contract если breaking |

**Rationale:** balance между **security velocity** (patches быстро) и **risk minimization** (major versions deliberate).

---

## 2. Tooling

### 2.1. Dependabot (GitHub native)

`.github/dependabot.yml`:

```yaml
version: 2
updates:
  - package-ecosystem: "<npm|pip|cargo|gomod>"
    directory: "/"
    schedule:
      interval: "weekly"
      day: "monday"
    groups:
      # Group patch updates for automerge
      patch-updates:
        update-types: ["patch"]
      # Minor/major separate PRs
      minor-updates:
        update-types: ["minor"]
    labels:
      - "dependencies"
    open-pull-requests-limit: 10
```

### 2.2. Renovate (alt, more configurable)

`renovate.json`:

```json
{
  "extends": ["config:recommended"],
  "packageRules": [
    {
      "matchUpdateTypes": ["patch"],
      "automerge": true,
      "automergeType": "branch"
    },
    {
      "matchUpdateTypes": ["minor"],
      "automerge": false
    },
    {
      "matchUpdateTypes": ["major"],
      "automerge": false,
      "labels": ["major-update"]
    }
  ],
  "vulnerabilityAlerts": {
    "automerge": true,
    "schedule": ["at any time"]
  }
}
```

### 2.3. Native tools (для local manual updates)

```sh
# Node
pnpm outdated
pnpm update --interactive

# Python (Poetry)
poetry show --outdated
poetry update

# Rust
cargo outdated
cargo update

# Go
go list -m -u all
go get -u ./...
```

См. `dev-environment.md` § 7 для project-specific Makefile targets.

